body_html: Looks like you didn't set return_indices=True on MaxPool2D. In most cases, this would throw an error when unpacking out, indices = self.pool(tmp), but if the output's 0th dim has size two it wouldn't throw.

body: Looks like you didn't set `return_indices=True` on MaxPool2D. In most cases, this would throw an error when unpacking `out, indices = self.pool(tmp)`, but if the output's 0th dim has size two it wouldn't throw.
